|YKOThe Darkwind Party System allows players to join groups of 2-6
players in order to combine their efforts battling against the
dangers of Darkwind. No longer is this ability contained in a
simple object that can be lost or misplaced, but is now part
of the essence of every adventurer. While in a party, you may
communicate easily with your fellows, gain a share of experience
from each others' kills, and, at your option, split any
earned gold. The following commands relate to the party system:|YKB

epsay           partyhist       pauto        pautosplit
pboot           pemote          pfollow      pleader
pleave          pname           poffer       psay
psplit          pstatus         preset

|YKOTo get more information on a command, use |YKB"help <command>"
